cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with processing surveillance videos, which is a common application of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses compressive sensing, which is a signal processing technique, making cs.MM (Mathematical Methods) and cs.IT (Information Theory) likely sub-categories. The paper also involves matrix decomposition, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing).
